PHOTO BEAUTY PLUS Privacy Policy
This privacy policy designates how any information you give us while using our apps

Your privacy is very important to us, and we take it seriously.

COLLECTION AND USE OF INFORMATION

    Personal information
    We do not collect information that allows direct association with any specific individual. Instead, we use the Android Advertising ID(or cookies) and anonymouse information in order to show ads and collect usage information. When you use our app your device automatically sends certain information to our partner. This information includes, for example, the name of the app, the device type, and the Android Advertising ID.
    Non-personal information
    We may collect non-personal information, such as data that does not allow association with any specific individual. Non-personal data is used to help improve the quality of our services and applications.
    Information you provide
    If you contact us for customer support, we may obtain and maintain any information you choose to provide, including your name, contact info such as your email address, as well as information about your mobile device or personal computer such as its device type, OS type, and logs. We will use this information to address and investigate the issues you have raised, to provide you support, and to improve our customer support service.

WE USE THE FOLLOWING THIRD PARTY SERVICES

        AdMob : How Google uses information from sites or apps that use our services
        Firebase : Privacy and Security in Firebase and Data collection


CHANGES TO OUR PRIVACY POLICY
We reserve the right to modify our Privacy Policy at any time simply by posting such modification on this site and without any other notification. Any such modification will be effective immediately upon posting on this site. It is your responsibility to review our Privacy Policy from time to time to ensure that you continue to agree with all of its terms.

